45 147;
46 (b) In the case of an individual, is a resident of this state as verified by
47 a 911 address or in the absence of a 911 system, a physical address; and
48 (c) Owns or rents agricultural property and principal place of business
49 is located in this state.
50 3. (1) For all tax years beginning on or after January 1, 2009, but
51 ending on or before December 31, 2021, a taxpayer shall be allowed a tax
